<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:note>
<db:para>There is no binary compatibility guarantee for this class, meaning that an application using it is only guaranteed to work with the Qt version it was developed against.</db:para>
</db:note>
<db:note>
<db:para>Due to being public while relying on otherwise hidden EGL types, this header itself does not include <db:code>EGL/egl.h</db:code>. It is the application's responsibility to include egl.h with any appropriate defines (for example, <db:code>MESA_EGL_NO_X11_HEADERS</db:code> or other vendor-specific defines controlling the typedefs for EGL's native resources) before this header.</db:para>
</db:note>
